A4.text: Commandaria is an amber-coloured sweet dessert wine made in the Commandaria region of Cyprus on the foothills of the Troödos Mountains.

A5.text: Commandaria is made exclusively from two types of indigenous Cyprus grapes: Xynisteri and Mavro.
